info.title: Calibration Session
info.description: The service Calibration Session allows you to get and update information of sessions and of a single subject or multiple subjects. You can find your company's API server in [List of API Servers in SAP SuccessFactors](https://help.sap.com/docs/SAP_SUCCESSFACTORS_PLATFORM/bdf1755a26754ab5a1c59e237d0e54f3/af2b8d5437494b12be88fe374eba75b6.html?locale=en-US).
